e location and population (Mycenae versus Asia Minor) used to be a matter of great contention. Based F. Sommer’s influential text edition of 1932, six researchers from different disciplines have now developed a revised version reflecting the state of research today.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aHittite languagevTexts. 0aHittite literaturevTranslations into German. 0aHittites. 4aAhhiawafrage. 4aDiplomatie. 4aHethiter. 4aPiyamaradu.  aAhhiawa.  aHittites.  aPiyamaradu.  adiplomacy.1 aHawkins, J. D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHawkins, John David.1 aHawkins, Mitwirkung von J. D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHazenbos, J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHazenbos, Jost.1 aHeinhold-Krahmer, S., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeinhold-Krahmer, Susanne, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMiller, Ergänzungen von J. L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMiller, J. L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMiller, Jared.1 aRieken, E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRieken, Elisabeth, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWeeden, M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWeeden, Mark.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAsian Studies Contemporary Collection eBook Packagez978311064982608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theology, Reli